"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>명령어 처리</h2>\n<p>아래의 명령어를 통해 처리한다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> /etc/localtime\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">ln</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-s</span> /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Seoul /etc/localtime</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"aws-추천-방법---amazon-time-sync-service-구성-처리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#aws-%EC%B6%94%EC%B2%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95---amazon-time-sync-service-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1-%EC%B2%98%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"aws 추천 방법   amazon time sync service 구성 처리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AWS 추천 방법 - Amazon Time Sync Service 구성 처리</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># Step 1 - 아래 커맨드 수행\nsudo apt install chrony\n\n# Step 2 - /etc/chrony/chrony.conf 파일 수정\nvim /etc/chrony/chrony.conf\n\n# Step 3 - 파일에 이미 존재하는 server 또는 pool 문 앞에 다음 라인을 추가하고 변경 사항을 저장\nserver 169.254.169.123 prefer iburst minpoll 4 maxpoll 4\n\n# Step 4 - chrony 서비스 재시작\nsudo /etc/init.d/chrony restart\n\n# Step 5 - 확인\nchronyc sources -v</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/set-time.html#configure-amazon-time-service-ubuntu\">참고링크</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toc\"><pre class=\"language-toc\"><code class=\"language-toc\"></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98\">주의</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4-%EB%AC%B8%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%80-%EA%B3%BC%EA%B1%B0-hexo-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-2021-10-03-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EB%8F%99%EB%90%9C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">이 문건은 과거 Hexo 블로그 (2021-10-03) 에서 이동된 문서입니다.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#aws-ec2-ubuntu%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%ED%83%80%EC%9E%84%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EB%A7%9E%EC%B6%94%EA%B8%B0\">Aws ec2 ubuntu에서 타임라인 맞추기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4-%EC%B2%98%EB%A6%AC\">명령어 처리</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#aws-%EC%B6%94%EC%B2%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95---amazon-time-sync-service-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1-%EC%B2%98%EB%A6%AC\">AWS 추천 방법 - Amazon Time Sync Service 구성 처리</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"aws ec2 ubuntu에서 타임라인 맞추기","description":null,"date":"October 03, 2021","tags":["Ubuntu","Aws","EC2"],"series":"Ubuntu","previewImage":"ubuntu_logo.png","isPrivate":null,"writer":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/java/190923_java-singleton/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Java에서 싱글톤(Singleton) 패턴을 사용하는 이유와 주의할 점","isPrivate":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/ubuntu/211003_rsa_key_change/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"RSA 키 충돌 (REMOTE HOST IDENTIFICATION HAS CHANGED)","isPrivate":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"bb1e5eab-b8b2-53ec-a4c1-78e6e61ce11b","previousPostId":"ac74f25b-a7f2-55bc-915f-3565f26239f4","nextPostId":"1b169a97-2259-5f63-8978-4cc9dfb9f466"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}